# Summary
This documentation details the TikTok Ads integration with Amplitude, allowing businesses to send audience cohorts to TikTok for personalized ad campaigns, retargeting, and suppression lists, with specific requirements for user property mapping to TikTok keys (IDFA, GAID, Email, Phone) and limitations including a 4.8 million user sync limit and 24 API calls per day per audience.

